            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Mandatory Basic Health Insurance (KVG/LAMal)</h3>
            
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">The cornerstone of the Swiss healthcare framework is the mandatory basic health insurance, known as <span class="font-medium">Grundversicherung</span> in German, <span class="font-medium">Assurance de base</span> in French, and <span class="font-medium">Assicurazione di base</span> in Italian. This is governed by the Swiss Federal Health Insurance Act (KVG/LAMal).</p>
            
